[mute]
!mute <playerName> [<duration>] [<type>] - mutes a player in game, until the end of the game or for <duration> minutes if specified
"!mute joe" mutes joe in game until the end of the game
"!mute joe 60" mutes joe in game for 1 hour
"!mute joe draw" mutes joe regarding draw actions only, until the end of the game
"!mute joe 30 chat" mutes joe regarding chat messages only, for 30 minutes

[mutes]
!mutes - lists current in-game mutes

[unmute]
!unmute <playerName> - unmutes a player in game
"!unmute joe" unmutes joe in game